[38:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'this with a 10x compression ratio, which basically means if you have like a,000 text tokens, you would just convert it into 100 vision tokens. So it\'s 10 times fewer tokens. If you do that, then the'

[38:49] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'model achieves very high decoding precision at around 97%. So it\'s nearly a 10 times lossless compression. And if you want to compress this further, so'

[39:01] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
