[39:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'here it\'s kind of a trade-off between efficiency and accuracy. And here\'s the advantage of using this OCR instead of just breaking text down into text tokens because we are essentially taking a'

[39:27] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
